3DpiFS--hJktc&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=541851c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=piFS--hJktc</a><br />\n睇下譚文豪去美國遊說, 根本都係唔想美國制裁香港官員, 但佢自己又唔敢講出來.<br />\n<br />\n既然你班民主鬥士出晒聲話冇事, 中國好好, 我地要民主回歸, 外國咪坐o係度唔出聲囉. 你話佢冇negative impact? 用下你個腦啦."},{"pid":"5ff635bd2d205c23f1ac7304714af3b32523a05a","tid":2313614,"uid":57797,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:14:57.000Z","msg":"楊岳橋一個就夠了 之前口響響 依家應該淆晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff50ae8a3a1b0dc66c24c49106a067ef9ebcf008","tid":2313614,"uid":214906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:17:04.000Z","msg":"國安試水溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b853b2d7d703fee6cdc2f8c7e5a560db519434a2","tid":2313614,"uid":86509,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:18:27.000Z","msg":"無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f31ca01efa4bb926dc40b401b849622f09118a","tid":2313614,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:20:50.000Z","msg":"露底啦 死藍絲 上左年紀果然冇個好人"},{"pid":"0ab01321715e3786cb64c0948bf21d00476d4460","tid":2313614,"uid":51583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"大陸式思維<br />\n自己唔鍾意既冇犯法都可以拉佢咁<br />\nON9 POST"},{"pid":"87092e48ea0c95b99d2a67a0c7ea418c09ce0997","tid":2313614,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"我自己就覺得wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36eb99e1437d83d0fd13757aed742542333d30af","tid":2313614,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebebd2327ce02fac7a721168cec1ad79cec9863f","tid":2313614,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"想佢地感受下法治，之前咁撚串"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"其實圍內都有唔